data.description: Beautiful open concept living with all the lovely upgrades! The pristine wood floors,upgraded granite counter tops,spacious master bedroom and huge master bath make this split floor plan the perfect home.Office area & formal dining open, lots of light.Covered front porch for sunsets or large covered back porch for entertaining surrounded by trees, nature and privacy.Home is 100% masonry,so no painting! Easy care landscaping with pathway from garage to back porch.Garage has steel cabinets & fresh paint.
